      "gap": 28,
      "padding": [
        48,
        56
      ],
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "icoT1",
          "name": "docTitle",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "content": "解语 Jieyu — 图标系统",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 40,
          "fontWeight": "800",
          "letterSpacing": -0.4
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "icoT2",
          "name": "docSub",
          "fill": "#666666",
          "content": "濒危语言科研协作 · 本地优先 · 线框工具气质；与左侧栏 17px 槽、波形区控件对齐。",
          "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "500"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "icoSpec",
          "name": "规范-section",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#FFFFFF",
          "cornerRadius": 14,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "#D8D4CC"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 12,
          "padding": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "icoS0",
              "name": "specH",
              "fill": "#2B2B2B",
              "content": "一、绘制规范（落地到 SVG / 组件）",
              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
              "fontSize": 18,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "icoS1",
              "name": "specB1",
              "fill": "#444444",
              "content": "• 逻辑画布 24×24，导出时随 CSS 缩放；线端圆角、拐角圆角，与现有 Lucide 用法一致。",
              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "icoS2",
              "name": "specB2",
              "fill": "#444444",
              "content": "• 默认描边 2px（视觉权重与 --text-primary 一致）；禁止在 17px 槽内超过 2 层嵌套轮廓，避免糊成一团。",
              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "icoS3",
              "name": "specB3",
              "fill": "#444444",
              "content": "• 语义：转写 = 时间中的话语；标注 = 结构化层叠；分析 = 模式/洞察；写作 = 草稿与叙述；词表 = 典藏条目。",
              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "icoS4",
              "name": "specB4",
              "fill": "#444444",
              "content": "• 社区共创扩展：成员/邀请/讨论/动态 使用独立隐喻，与「档案」图标区分；双色块仅用于主 CTA，勿铺满导航。",
              "fontFamily": "Noto Sans SC",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
